{"tid":2441524,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"資本主義同共產主義文明所催生的 “人死如燈滅” 觀念","createTime":"2021-03-10T18:17:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T00:51:01.000Z","uid":47901,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"63726e982331f0a4adb02c3423c29bb5d73be3f1","tid":2441524,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T18:17:05.000Z","msg":"在近現代的兩大經濟主義陣營對壘之前的時代，&ldquo;人死如燈滅&rdquo; 觀念是幾乎不存在於人類的各種的文明同社會之中，上至大帝國，下至原始部落都是<br />\n<br />\n但是為甚麼在兩大主義陣營開始對壘之時，這觀念會發展得如火如荼呢？<br />\n<br />\n因為這兩種主義企圖以截然不同的方式去提升經濟生產力，以此作為宗旨手段去實現烏托邦，所以必須要將人們對於此一生以外的所有生命世界觀念完全摒棄，才能使到人們全力以赴地在現世生命的時光中，拼命生產去共同建立經濟生產的烏托邦<br />\n<br />\n春蠶到死絲方盡，蠟炬成灰淚始乾<br />\n<br />\n既然人們觀念中，生命的所有意義都只在現世生命，人們便會追求現世生命的&ldquo;最大程度地發光發亮&rdquo;，在以經濟手段為宗旨去實現烏托邦的理念下，就促成人們一窩蜂地拼命地投入生產崗位，並且人所得的 &ldquo;玩具&rdquo; 亦只會在其現世生命時光內有任何意義<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kaHFHxu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkaHFHxu.jpg&h=6f0aa808&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2o076Y9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2o076Y9.jpg&h=02631e35&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d4961a704b66bab3687176a9e6f726d223eeeacd","tid":2441524,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T18:32:03.000Z","msg":"甚至，許多&ldquo;宗教&rdquo;在資本主義理念的大氛圍底下，會墮落到變成商業機構，牟利機構，公司等等....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6_aIwaLT9KI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6_aIwaLT9KI&d=86rwbh%2BN0C2BU4li7ttIPgsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=30178164\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6_aIwaLT9KI</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hx_PNfiikPA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fhx_PNfiikPA&d=86rwbh%2BN0C2BU4li7ttIPgsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=9f949e40\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hx_PNfiikPA</a>"},{"pid":"4e9002593cb8dff4130f9c7ab5b85d2199badf5c","tid":2441524,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T18:45:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/7N7DNCgWQIs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7N7DNCgWQIs&d=86rwbh%2BN0C2BU4li7ttIPgsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=89e3694b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7N7DNCgWQIs</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/EfskK_MS_14\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FEfskK_MS_14&d=86rwbh%2BN0C2BU4li7ttIPgsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=9571a476\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/EfskK_MS_14</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/tBWqYwDf7_I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FtBWqYwDf7_I&d=86rwbh%2BN0C2BU4li7ttIPgsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=ddf03ce3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/tBWqYwDf7_I</a>"},{"pid":"e73b9f4770165d7746600d8ea2255653e8064c83","tid":2441524,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T19:12:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d804bd96df8d8d58bcf6c6cef7c5dbe22292b67","tid":2441524,"uid":158270,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T20:13:18.000Z","msg":"物化人類生產力係封建秩序瓦解嘅體現，因為人擁有嘅身份減少，價值會趨向單一同質嘅勞力。<br />\n但發生呢件事嘅原因唔係資本主義同共產主義。上述情況係封建主義瓦解後，資本主義制度代替經濟制度嘅過程；共產主義則係資本主義嘅挑戰者，爭奪封建社會崩潰後嘅權力真空。資本主義只係填補經濟制度不足導致嘅真空，冇主動淘空人嘅內在價值。"},{"pid":"e38faae1474a920692aea866dc53d7cd615e72c4","tid":2441524,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2d804bd96df8d8d58bcf6c6cef7c5dbe22292b67","tid":2441524,"uid":158270,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T20:13:18.000Z","msg":"物化人類生產力係封建秩序瓦解嘅體現，因為人擁有嘅身份減少，價值會趨向單一同質嘅勞力。<br />\n但發生呢件事嘅原因唔係資本主義同共產主義。上述情況係封建主義瓦解後，資本主義制度代替經濟制度嘅過程；共產主義則係資本主義嘅挑戰者，爭奪封建社會崩潰後嘅權力真空。資本主義只係填補經濟制度不足導致嘅真空，冇主動淘空人嘅內在價值。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T21:49:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\"