托邦，所以必須要將人們對於此一生以外的所有生命世界觀念完全摒棄，才能使到人們全力以赴地在現世生命的時光中，拼命生產去共同建立經濟生產的烏托邦<br />\n<br />\n春蠶到死絲方盡，蠟炬成灰淚始乾<br />\n<br />\n既然人們觀念中，生命的所有意義都只在現世生命，人們便會追求現世生命的&ldquo;最大程度地發光發亮&rdquo;，在以經濟手段為宗旨去實現烏托邦的理念下，就促成人們一窩蜂地拼命地投入生產崗位，並且人所得的 &ldquo;玩具&rdquo; 亦只會在其現世生命時光內有任何意義<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kaHFHxu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkaHFHxu.jpg&h=6f0aa808&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2o076Y9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2o076Y9.jpg&h=02631e35&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最根源係因為人類<strong>看唔見有靈魂/上帝/神靈/鬼魂/佛。</strong><strong>顯微鏡也沒法看到</strong>這些超自然生命和靈魂。<strong>科學儀器也沒法偵測到</strong>靈魂/上帝/神靈/鬼魂/佛。<br />\n<br />\n其次係因為<strong>太多神棍騙食，宗教騙子。</strong><br />\n<br />\n再其次係因為世上太多宗教，且<strong>宗教之間的教義有明顯矛盾</strong>，例如基督教話只有耶和華是神，耶穌是神的兒子，不信耶和華和耶穌得不到永生，且要下地獄。伊斯蘭教就話只有阿拉係神，其他係假神偶像，不能拜祂們。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"f33f0d6c5e94be1e5322ee86e477e6f802bf1ea1","tid":2441524,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:54:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11eec96d659cd8b4d33f1f4612711f81106b8c43","tid":2441524,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T15:27:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/N3xSY_Mj56M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FN3xSY_Mj56M&d=86rwbh%2BN0C2BU4li7ttIPgsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=5498810b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/N3xSY_Mj56M</a>"},{"pid":"3ab5a610352fbc6a507c30b22256c1edec813fdc","tid":2441524,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T16:39:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/awake.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21948c111da768e928f7b66a869b9cf46803d94e","tid":2441524,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T2